                <para styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-2DCam-ParametersTab" anchor="2DCAM-DIALOG-LIFETIME-PROPERTIES" styleclass="VariableName">Parameters tab &gt;</link><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-2DCam-ParametersTab" styleclass="Separator"> Enable Lifetimes, Edit Safety-Factor</link><text styleclass="Separator">&#32;</text>&#32;</para>
